    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes a Conservation Agriculture and Soil Health Incentive Program within the Hawaii Climate Change Mitigation and Adaptation Commission.  Requires an annual report to the Legislature.  Appropriates funds.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
